8a1575b8-64cb-4576-883b-6928a90c1736.title: Armour salesman
8a1575b8-64cb-4576-883b-6928a90c1736.text: And to you. Can I help you?

options.text: I'd like to see what you sell.
Can you tell me about your cape?

a1ce8268-e6fc-492e-bb0f-f7a58ce7698b.title: Armour salesman
a1ce8268-e6fc-492e-bb0f-f7a58ce7698b.text:
I am a supplier of leather armours and accessories. Ask
and I will tell you what I know.

44c16098-4c27-4b78-ae61-e939e2450494.title: Armour salesman
44c16098-4c27-4b78-ae61-e939e2450494.text: I have normal, studded and hard types.

1618af94-621a-4f8f-a66e-8c32d3d7aa16.title: Armour salesman
1618af94-621a-4f8f-a66e-8c32d3d7aa16.text:
Indeed, leather armour is excellent for archers. It's
supple and not very heavy.

605b592a-4066-47d4-bc7a-c4991355e298.title: Armour salesman
605b592a-4066-47d4-bc7a-c4991355e298.text:
Ah, now that's leather covered with studs. It's more
protective than ordinary leather.

4684e084-5822-4c20-ae6c-145be63f83ab.title: Armour salesman
4684e084-5822-4c20-ae6c-145be63f83ab.text:
Hard leather is specially treated using oils and drying
methods to create a hard-wearing armour.

e67c5390-5c26-4d72-833b-b00389f63053.title: Armour salesman
e67c5390-5c26-4d72-833b-b00389f63053.text:
Ah yes we have a new range of accessories in stock.
Essential items for an archer like you.

4646d772-e928-4317-9040-c21aaf3f049f.title: Armour salesman
4646d772-e928-4317-9040-c21aaf3f049f.text: We have vambraces, chaps, cowls and coifs.

bcc51be7-1634-4210-b8c2-e6a10018a4cf.title: Armour salesman
bcc51be7-1634-4210-b8c2-e6a10018a4cf.text:
Ah yes, vambraces. These useful items are for your
arms.

d870cb4b-3d19-4742-82cd-4232ec5354f6.title: Armour salesman
d870cb4b-3d19-4742-82cd-4232ec5354f6.text:
A protective sheath that favours the bow and arrow. An
essential purchase.

63891a6b-92d5-4028-bdd3-dd0aaf19d606.title: Armour salesman
63891a6b-92d5-4028-bdd3-dd0aaf19d606.text:
Chaps have two functions: firstly to protect your legs,
and secondly for ease of reloading arrows.

1e53fc47-740f-47e0-b5bb-63d6f27c31bc.title: Armour salesman
1e53fc47-740f-47e0-b5bb-63d6f27c31bc.text:
I can highly recommend these to you for quick
archery.

9c2a4670-25cc-4f60-8d81-a0c7550fbe34.title: Armour salesman
9c2a4670-25cc-4f60-8d81-a0c7550fbe34.text:
The cowl is a soft leather hat, ideal for protection with
maneuverability.

06ad7796-c02c-4190-a561-0c37f6e1ca58.title: Armour salesman
06ad7796-c02c-4190-a561-0c37f6e1ca58.text: These are highly favoured with our guards.

20dff08f-e2b0-460f-8b26-00b04f55f405.title: Armour salesman
20dff08f-e2b0-460f-8b26-00b04f55f405.text:
The coif is a specialized cowl, that has extra chain
protection to keep your neck and shoulders safe.

cb9ea8b4-95fa-499c-84b7-533fd45b9fc0.title: Armour salesman
cb9ea8b4-95fa-499c-84b7-533fd45b9fc0.text: An excellent addition to our range, traveller.

db3d064e-912a-45f6-a19e-2733e13266e6.title: <player>
db3d064e-912a-45f6-a19e-2733e13266e6.text: I'd like to see what you sell.

8f21a6a2-8a4d-4af3-8dcb-2e33334ab9b2.title: Armour salesman
8f21a6a2-8a4d-4af3-8dcb-2e33334ab9b2.text: Indeed, cast your eyes on my wares, adventurer.

39095210-0886-4394-85e0-08fa46a699e3.title: <player>
39095210-0886-4394-85e0-08fa46a699e3.text: Can you tell me about your cape?

fe59953e-7cd4-45d6-a541-ebf4a797e23f.title: Armour salesman
fe59953e-7cd4-45d6-a541-ebf4a797e23f.text:
Certainly! Skillcapes are a symbol of achievement. Only
people who have mastered a skill and reached level 99
can get their hands on them and gain the benefits they
carry.

cd1c41c1-3b7b-4aa6-8b71-1ea9de2605a9.title: Armour salesman
cd1c41c1-3b7b-4aa6-8b71-1ea9de2605a9.text:
The Cape of Ranging has been modified by Ava to
function as one of her accumulator devices. Is there
anything else I can help you with?
